---
title: Bacon-Wrapped Green Beans with Horseradish Dip
description: For this easy yet indulgent appetizer, crisp, smoky bacon encases tender green beans, creating a mouthwatering blend of flavours. Paired with a zesty horseradish dipper, they're a welcome addition with a little kick.

